CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season - Attractive Guests - Among the out-of-towners attending the Frogs' swank formal at the Gateway Plaza last Friday were these attractive guests. Clockwise: Dr. Benjamin Bullock of Buffalo, N.Y.; Mrs. Edward Clark and Mr. Clark of Buffalo; Mrs. Albert Garland and Mr. Garland, McKeesport; Mrs. Scipio White and Mr. White of Monessen and Mrs. Bullock of Buffalo.  They were the guests of the Percy Garlands. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, seated clockwise: Dr. Benjamin Bullock, Mr. and Mrs. Edward Clark, Mr. and Mrs. Albert Garland, Mr. and Mrs. Scipio White, and Mrs. Benjamin Bullock, in Gateway Plaza for FROGS formal
